{"type": "article", "id": 6509, "title": "如何把蓝天沙滩海鸥拍出不一样的感觉", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 8, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t电影制作人<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/parkerpaul\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;font-variant:inherit;font-stretch:inherit;line-height:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;\">保罗·帕克</a>（Paul Parker）最近发布了一部希区柯克式的延时摄影视频 “海鸥拉线”（Seagull Skytrails），拍摄了一群海鸥在英国西南康沃尔郡的海边乘风飞翔的镜头。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#1F0909;font-family:'PT Serif';line-height:24px;white-space:normal;\">由于使用了 After Effects 软件的“重影效果”（echo effect）制作，</span><span style=\"font-family:'sans serif', tahoma, verdana, helvetica;\">旅游小城圣艾维斯（St. Ives）的天空中的</span><span style=\"color:#1F0909;font-family:'PT Serif';line-height:24px;\"><span style=\"color:#1F0909;font-family:'PT Serif';line-height:24px;\">海鸥飞翔路线被显现了出来。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#1F0909;font-family:'PT Serif';line-height:24px;\"><span style=\"color:#1F0909;font-family:'PT Serif';line-height:24px;\"> \r\n\t<iframe height=\"498\" width=\"640\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/embed/XODkyNDY0MTA0\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\">\r\n\t</iframe>\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#1F0909;font-family:'PT Serif';line-height:24px;\"><span style=\"color:#1F0909;font-family:'PT Serif';line-height:24px;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160604214001VPpEq9ed7C81sN0x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t虽然是蓝天白云、海鸥飞翔，但小清新的感觉也是一秒变深邃，还有点小阴森。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t原文来自：http://www.vice.cn/read/swooping-seagull-flight-paths-revealed-in-time-blended-video\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<a href=\"http://www.vice.cn\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20160604214001GI8eACFNkJHOXBwn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.24242424\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}